metadata.name: voice sounded in my head
metadata.description:
silence, the King said, "Fairy King."



Nicknames sometimes really kill people, and the last life is related to his nickname.



After the blue star data, there are many new races, among which there are immortal people, people are immortal people, you called 'Fairy king', this is not to add to others?



Although for some reasons, the immortal clan could not kill him openly, they stabbed Wang Xian from the back in the first war, so that he died on the battlefield.



When they were finally killed, the faeries revealed a secret.
